src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCwAcwcu.jpg&h=58daabfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n物資<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y9WrGxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy9WrGxN.jpg&h=74ccea60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 屯門政府合署前地 1300集合<br />\n2. 荃灣沙咀道球場 1300集合<br />\n3. 修頓球場 1300集結<br />\n4. 沙田車公廟前地 1130配合和理suck<br />\n5. 黃大仙廣場 1300集合 1330起步<br />\n黃大仙道-&gt;窩打老道-&gt;在界限街和彌敦道交界停下<br />\n6. 深水埗楓樹街球場 1300集合 1430起步<br />\n沿長沙灣道走 在長沙灣道和彌敦道交界停下<br />\n在交界會師後 1500-1530 沿彌敦道向尖沙咀方向出發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十一國殤 六區開花<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600404</a>"},{"pid":"38afeaedefded85af1e63dd3aea37aa68ce9c74c","tid":1606053,"uid":94435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:54:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"62d43b7fda13b0a1a2437d712f0589b24ae3037c","tid":1606053,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:54:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"68d9455ac8041cc4557c2145a47dba98a098fcda","tid":1606053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ec072b5ff44b52b116715205f370c167e24b10","tid":1606053,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a842f1a9c8288926a803020539483b1c15d7f522","tid":1606053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"水炮車 *3  = 中聯辦 *1、政總 *1、機場 *1<br />\n<br />\n三部水炮車不足夠應付六區，所以當水炮車清左政總場後<br />\n水炮車好大機會移動到其他區清場<br />\n大家呢個時候就要表達Be Water精粹<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n水炮車清政總場，港島人安全散開<br />\n水炮車移動到九龍，九龍人安全散開<br />\n港島人再出嚟強攻政總，無限LOOP<br />\n<br />\nMON PO 狗睇完之後可能唔敢調防，咁到時其他區任玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之Be Water，睇資訊，拎任務，對準政權，唔好做圍狗屋等低效手段，<br />\n參考任務可睇下面<br />\n<br />\n各區Channel整合如下：<br />\n⚠️灣仔