辦九龍部（觀塘海濱道135號宏碁資本大廈22樓）<br />\n（５）黨鐵總部<br />\n（６）中旅社（得寶大廈3樓／常悅道9號企業廣場一期202室）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">沙田：目標</span></strong><br />\n（１）中聯辦新界部（沙田小瀝源源順圍28號都會廣場R1&mdash;R4）<br />\n（２）中旅社（沙田娛樂城地下B舖）<br />\n（３）馬場（和你SUCK 5.0）<br />\n【國慶行動】【主線解說】【SUCK小隊】10.1 SUCK泥馬 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1596683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1596683</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">荃灣：目標</span></strong><br />\n（１）機場（和你SUCK 5.0，Mon Post狗你估下我地會唔會入機場）<br />\n（２）中旅社（青山公路(荃灣段)189號地下）<br />\n（３）二阪坊？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">屯門：目標</span></strong><br />\n（１）中旅社（嘉華大廈1/F A舖 ）<br />\n（２）何君堯<br />\n（３）南邊圍？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"灣仔：中銀大廈！"},{"pid":"f47d09c23235f3cd064314898480071fc9452653","tid":1606053,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:57:27.000Z","msg":"大家聽日要有目標！唔好再賽跑啦！記得保護自己保護手足<br />\n<br />\n《終極軍師》勇武請入，十一「六區佔領政府部門」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605991</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bd0b308bdd2f5ba06020d9f2cb5eeaedd8e53132","tid":1606053,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日出去前睇左先</span></span></span><br />\n來自CSD職員既提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你班勇武手足,同我聽住,有部份前線手足認識我地,之前幾場戰役我地合作過,最初有人以為我地係鬼,詳細唔多講,我地係一班受過專業防暴訓練懲教署職員,之前已經係現場教過大家,如何組織防線同攻擊防暴,之前都有唔少進步,但今日我地冇出現,你地表現太差,中要咁多比人拉,我好心痛..<br />\n我地人手有限,身份問題,冇可能次次出現,我係度比些少資訊大家,希望大家務必share同發輝得好D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.速龍都係人,佢地咩住咁重裝備同蒙面先至令信心大增,但大家留意下佢地人手一定唔夠手足多,只要大家穩固防線,只要佢地一跑出嚟,手足唔走向前攻,先用人火同磚頭攻,再快速向前推進, 趁機會足幾個差人抬去自己方向,呢個時候繼續用磚頭攻擊,同時向差人方向口射洗潔精地下,務別令佢地仆街,最重要立即除佢哋面具,之後私了..佢地以後就會驚..</span></span><br />\n2.佩槍唔係向上蚊,而係向內45度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..</span></span><br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<br />\n一班CSD職員上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xha9fC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xha9fC.jpg&h=c177bd82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZPXPfD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZPXPfD.jpg&h=815c41fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0158e742a43335b7d14042e4f2547f7d1b661e9f","tid":1606053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3204fa58bd51c6a167d8ec37b4a54f7815a2f1","tid":1606053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0a5bf080434523e7018241dc98b2f1c5c4da3c","tid":1606053,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"be water"},{"pid":"639e4bd7ea039b331466e187c57b989739e77d8b","tid":1606053,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"660d3400836df2d28b59d8e91523d9b13ed50d14","tid":1606053,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔知我有無聽錯，十月一日皇上閱兵期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">假如同一時間有遊行，係絕對唔會有清場行動。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">聽講北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令皇上即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。但之前上面會嚇窒唔俾大家出，但如果出咗佢都耐你唔何。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">聽講十一閱兵期間嘅和平遊行，唔會有清場鎮壓！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585568\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585568</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核彈！中共極懼怕網絡信息安全在國慶節前出事！兄弟們即刻行動香港可獲勝！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1574727\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1574727</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「天滅中共！習近平全家死」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee278ce94740748f19a607901b7d41bab3d6bcf6","tid":1606053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae53e66dde4c85c124f9cf7c10188af20139ccca","tid":1606053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5287ed1b479bc4a1f8bd7aed436889d701c3f3c4","tid":1606053,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af68643362942ea512e61c1627290def7f78ebc1","tid":1606053,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"咁都算推演咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe0498cfb996052f9b374e0e2d86f4a9feb6bfa","tid":1606053,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"有冇可能唔六區開花<br />\n但係香港九龍一齊大遊行？<br />\n一係就六區每區都搵個目標"},{"pid":"6ff96febe355f5d5ca8be797409d4a26794f0486","tid":1606053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca7d397634275d205216f2526457df2d4da26f6","tid":1606053,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGVTmzV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGVTmzV.jpg&h=c9cd4e99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24e95568a2577c3aeaf87001de65f23de47a8fb0","tid":1606053,"uid":267423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0efac27e55ab633a7ffa8ed701a598b641e68afd","tid":1606053,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"建制派office<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1088f7bef9e4c79d64b8e58e16fc26fc036385d","tid":1606053,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fda26f30a541954de838ad974e13dc0d51731e","tid":1606053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e8b815f27833400989a2e40382ff9436d7c5a5","tid":1606053,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}